data.eml:eml: Taxonomic study of subgenus Plastus s. str. (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Osoriinae) in China, with descriptions of five new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wu, Jie, Zhou, Hong-Zhang (2010): Taxonomic study of subgenus Plastus s. str. (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Osoriinae) in China, with descriptions of five new species.
